# Choosing a Text Editor 

## What is a *Text Editor?*

A *text editor* is software that can either be downloaded and installed on your computer *or* accessed online through a web browser. It allows web developers to write and manage text to build websites. 

## Features to Look for in a Text Editor 

1. Code Completion
  > Code Competeion allows for 
  
1. Syntax Highlighting
1. Nice Variety of Themes * (to reduce eye strain and fatigue)
1. Ability to choose for good selection of extentions
